column5: Hi all,  thinking about going to thornbury & Mayfield tomorrow for trout/steelhead ... salmon if any  any information?
Won't catch any sitting here...hit the road...let us know how it went!
Last report was ,water was low, and they are staged out from the mouths. Im thinking theres going to be a lake spawn. It has happen before.
I dont know about you guys but I hate the frustration when not catching anything after long drive!  any more information is welcome!

HMMMMMMM Did I not say the waters were low and the fish were staging out from the mouth? Man,Im driving 2 hours this weekend to hunt. I hope it,s not a WASTE of time sitting out in the bush,thinking about times past and enjoying the outdoors and friendship.
its hit or miss at best right now, water is way low and really clear.  Tons of guys.
